The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks in robotics and machine learning, specifically addressing the issue of catastrophic forgetting when updating established representations with new knowledge. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on image recognition tasks, cs.CV is the most likely category, followed by cs.LG and cs.AI.
